{
  "title": "Tender Roasted Middle Eastern Chwinamul Tagine",
  "description": "A tender and flavorful roasted Middle Eastern dish featuring chwinamul, perfect for a date night, and egg-free friendly. This recipe uses a fondue pot as the cooking vessel.",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
